582
00:26:04,079 --> 00:26:05,240
Mr. Liu, sorry

583
00:26:05,519 --> 00:26:06,160
to trouble you.

584
00:26:06,599 --> 00:26:07,880
No trouble at all.

585
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:08,640
It's on the way anyway.

586
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,599
Are you really going

587
00:26:12,599 --> 00:26:13,519
to Su City for a case?

588
00:26:13,839 --> 00:26:15,279
Yeah. A site visit.

589
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:18,640
An old classmate

590
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,319
of a client

591
00:26:20,759 --> 00:26:21,799
happens to be in Su City.

592
00:26:22,359 --> 00:26:23,720
You even have to interview old classmates?

593
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,480
That's rough.

594
00:26:26,559 --> 00:26:27,319
Tell me about it.

595
00:26:27,559 --> 00:26:29,279
Sometimes clients

596
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,200
can be really difficult.

597
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:33,839
Hey, Ruan Yu,
I saw the house location

598
00:26:34,839 --> 00:26:35,920
you sent me.

599
00:26:36,559 --> 00:26:37,839
It's very close to Xu Huaisong's

600
00:26:37,839 --> 00:26:38,519
grandma's place.

601
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,039
Xu Huaisong?

602
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:41,359
[My mom taught]

603
00:26:41,359 --> 00:26:42,559
[Xu Huaisong Chinese for half a year.]

604
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,079
[Would she still remember that?]

605
00:26:44,279 --> 00:26:45,200
[That'd blow my cover!]

606
00:26:46,039 --> 00:26:47,440
Really? What a coincidence.

607
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,599
Mom, when we get there,

608
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:51,039
do you want to try that...

609
00:26:51,119 --> 00:26:51,880
The name Xu Huaisong

610
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,920
sounds so familiar.

611
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,599
I can't remember at all.

612
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:55,839
It's okay, Mrs. Ruan.

613
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:58,119
Don't force yourself.

614
00:26:58,400 --> 00:26:59,400
It's not someone important.

615
00:27:00,119 --> 00:27:01,039
Just remember me.

616
00:27:01,559 --> 00:27:02,599
I remember you.

617
00:27:03,799 --> 00:27:04,759
I'm telling you,

618
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,000
getting older

619
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:06,880
is no joke.

620
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,440
I used to remember

621
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,519
every kid

622
00:27:09,759 --> 00:27:10,839
in the alleys

623
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:12,599
and all my old students.

624
00:27:13,759 --> 00:27:14,799
Now, so many

625
00:27:14,799 --> 00:27:16,119
of them have slipped my mind.

626
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:18,200
It's okay, Mom.

627
00:27:18,559 --> 00:27:20,079
My memory's not so great either.

628
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:21,400
See? You should

629
00:27:22,039 --> 00:27:23,559
spend less time on the computer.

630
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:25,799
You two keep chatting.

631
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:35,720
So, I've safely

632
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:36,960
delivered Yu

633
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:38,519
and her mother.

634
00:27:38,680 --> 00:27:39,400
You can rest easy.

635
00:27:40,119 --> 00:27:40,920
Also,

636
00:27:41,519 --> 00:27:43,160
got some intel for you.

637
00:27:44,279 --> 00:27:45,240
In the car,
I heard Mrs. Ruan say

638
00:27:46,119 --> 00:27:47,000
she's going back today

639
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,119
to meet up with some old colleagues.

640
00:27:48,599 --> 00:27:49,359
Not sure if Ruan Yu

641
00:27:49,359 --> 00:27:50,680
will stop by the school.

642
00:27:51,079 --> 00:27:52,559
Something to think about.

643
00:27:58,319 --> 00:27:59,240
Liu, the wingman,

644
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:00,559
mission accomplished!

645
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,039
Mom, it's raining.

646
00:28:09,279 --> 00:28:09,759
Use the umbrella.

647
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,400
See? I told you.

648
00:28:15,559 --> 00:28:16,400
Young as you are,

649
00:28:16,799 --> 00:28:17,759
sitting at the computer
all day, and you

650
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,319
get back pain at the slightest movement.

651
00:28:20,519 --> 00:28:21,039
What?

652
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,279
Are you as old as I am now?

653
00:28:24,319 --> 00:28:26,440
Message received.

654
00:28:26,759 --> 00:28:28,440
I'll start working out.

655
00:28:29,839 --> 00:28:30,359
Take a look.

656
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,960
Appreciate it while we can.

657
00:28:38,279 --> 00:28:39,200
I just can't bear
to part with these

658
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:41,240
old houses and flowers.

659
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:42,880
Back in the day,

660
00:28:43,599 --> 00:28:44,319
your father and I
got married here.

661
00:28:46,799 --> 00:28:47,720
You used to run all over

662
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:48,839
playing here when you

663
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:49,480
were little.
Remember?

664
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,240
I loved going there.

665
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:53,279
And you were chased by two dogs,

666
00:28:53,279 --> 00:28:53,799
remember?

667
00:28:57,279 --> 00:28:58,000
Come to think of it,
your grandparents

668
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:01,039
were still around back then.

669
00:29:04,759 --> 00:29:05,279
Mom,

670
00:29:06,039 --> 00:29:07,640
the memories are still

671
00:29:08,119 --> 00:29:09,000
here with us.

672
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:10,920
You know,

673
00:29:11,359 --> 00:29:12,039
we'll have fewer and fewer
chances to come back.

674
00:29:14,039 --> 00:29:15,039
That's not true.

675
00:29:15,359 --> 00:29:16,880
Transportation is so easy now.

676
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:18,680
I'll get a driver's license.

677
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,599
If you and dad want to come back,

678
00:29:20,839 --> 00:29:21,359
I can give you
a ride anytime.

679
00:29:22,759 --> 00:29:24,359
It's tiring for you to drive that long.

680
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:25,640
It'd be best

681
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,319
if my son-in-law

682
00:29:27,319 --> 00:29:28,640
did the driving.

683
00:29:29,160 --> 00:29:29,920
Mom,

684
00:29:31,039 --> 00:29:32,759
why do you bring that up again?

685
00:29:33,839 --> 00:29:34,759
I didn't want to
say anything in the car.

686
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,240
Actually, Mr. Liu

687
00:29:37,599 --> 00:29:38,079
already has

688
00:29:38,079 --> 00:29:39,440
a matchmaking date.

689
00:29:39,799 --> 00:29:40,519
So, don't go

690
00:29:40,799 --> 00:29:42,279
bothering him again.

691
00:29:43,119 --> 00:29:43,960
Really?

692
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,319
I thought he seemed

693
00:29:46,319 --> 00:29:47,240
kinda interested.
I thought...

694
00:29:49,279 --> 00:29:50,880
You already asked him,

695
00:29:51,039 --> 00:29:52,079
and he's

696
00:29:52,079 --> 00:29:53,440
a helpful person.

697
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:55,160
How could he say no?

698
00:29:55,799 --> 00:29:57,119
Now I feel bad.

699
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,920
Alright, it's fine.

700
00:29:59,519 --> 00:30:00,319
If he's taken,

701
00:30:00,559 --> 00:30:01,359
there'll be someone else.

702
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:02,880
I'll keep looking for you.

703
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:03,920
Alright,

704
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:05,480
you take your time.

705
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:07,799
I'm going to go get some water.

706
00:30:08,799 --> 00:30:09,319
Go ahead.

707
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:11,680
Let me enjoy the view.

708
00:30:11,839 --> 00:30:12,480
Sure, Mom.

709
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:13,519
Sir.

710
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,079
What do you need?

711
00:30:15,839 --> 00:30:16,359
Soy sauce.
Over there.

712
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:25,960
Sir,

713
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:27,599
which of these two

714
00:30:27,599 --> 00:30:28,920
is better for stir-fry?

715
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:30,759
The Ruan family, right?

716
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,440
Your parents use this one for stir-fry.

717
00:30:32,559 --> 00:30:33,759
This one works too.

718
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,799
What about for a dipping sauce?

719
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:37,079
Which is better?

720
00:30:37,359 --> 00:30:38,599
For dipping, let's see.

721
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:39,559
This one.

722
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:40,599
This works.

723
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:42,680
Is it just for dipping?

724
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,119
Can I use it for cold dishes?

725
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,119
Sure.

726
00:30:45,559 --> 00:30:46,920
You can use both for cold dishes.

727
00:30:48,519 --> 00:30:48,960
So...

728
00:30:50,039 --> 00:30:51,000
which of these two

729
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:52,200
is a better value?

730
00:30:52,519 --> 00:30:54,640
Which one won't stick to the pan?

731
00:30:55,319 --> 00:30:56,440
Let me take another look.

732
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:57,519
Thanks.

733
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,720
He finally looked at me.

734
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:09,119
But why does he

735
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,640
look at me like I'm an idiot?

736
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:23,039
Ten years.

737
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:25,119
Everything's changed.

738
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:29,720
Done yet?

739
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,119
Yes.

740
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:34,200
Sir, I'll take this one.

741
00:31:36,559 --> 00:31:37,440
Coming, Mom.

742
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,000
It cleared up!

743
00:31:45,319 --> 00:31:46,480
That's just how it is down south.

744
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:47,799
On and off.

745
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,480
It's almost noon.

746
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,599
Let's go grab something to eat.

747
00:31:50,799 --> 00:31:51,319
Sounds good.
What do you want?

748
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:53,599
You pick.
I'm fine with anything.

749
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:56,640
In that case,

750
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,480
I'm kinda craving the dishes from

751
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,119
the school cafeteria.

752
00:32:01,279 --> 00:32:03,400
Going to the school cafeteria at noon,

753
00:32:03,759 --> 00:32:04,680
I'll run right
into Xu Huaishi.

754
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:06,559
Mom,

755
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,240
let's go to that

756
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,200
Zhou's Steak House.

757
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,160
I've been craving it.

758
00:32:10,319 --> 00:32:11,720
You said you were fine with anything.

759
00:32:12,119 --> 00:32:13,200
The more I think about it,

760
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,440
the more I crave those

761
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,680
meatballs from the cafeteria.

762
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:16,440
They are so good.

763
00:32:16,839 --> 00:32:17,480
And I can

764
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:19,680
go catch up with

765
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,640
Ms. Guo and Ms. Li.

766
00:32:21,519 --> 00:32:22,599
So looking forward to it.

767
00:32:23,079 --> 00:32:24,240
It's settled. Let's go.

768
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:26,319
Little foodie.

769
00:32:26,559 --> 00:32:27,400
Eat your jelly.

770
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:31,039
Let's hit the cafeteria.

771
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,440
Grab the umbrella.

772
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,519
It might
rain again.

773
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,279
That's right.
Let's go.

774
00:32:45,119 --> 00:32:46,319
Being young is great.

775
00:32:47,119 --> 00:32:47,759
I always thought

776
00:32:47,759 --> 00:32:49,240
the uniform was ugly before.

777
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:51,640
Now I don't even get a chance to wear one.

778
00:32:52,599 --> 00:32:53,440
If you're not young anymore,
what does that make me?

779
00:32:55,079 --> 00:32:56,920
Mom, you're young.

780
00:32:57,079 --> 00:32:58,200
We're both young.

781
00:32:58,759 --> 00:32:59,799
Tell you what,

782
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:00,559
how about I go borrow

783
00:33:00,559 --> 00:33:01,920
two uniforms from them?

784
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:02,640
We can change into them.
Maybe someone will

785
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,079
come up and ask,

786
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:04,920
"Excuse me,

787
00:33:05,319 --> 00:33:06,359
how do I get to the art gallery?"

788
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:09,319
What did I teach you?

789
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:10,960
Sharp tongue.

790
00:33:11,279 --> 00:33:12,599
No shame.

791
00:33:12,759 --> 00:33:13,359
Well said.

792
00:33:15,559 --> 00:33:17,160
Ma'am, I'll take three drumsticks.

793
00:33:17,559 --> 00:33:18,599
-Alright.
-Hungry?

794
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:22,799
Ma'am,

795
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:25,240
is Mr. Cai

796
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,359
still working here?

797
00:33:27,279 --> 00:33:28,039
Which Mr. Cai?
The one

798
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:30,079
who used to

799
00:33:30,079 --> 00:33:30,799
update the menu.

800
00:33:33,039 --> 00:33:33,680
Not ringing a bell.

801
00:33:34,759 --> 00:33:35,440
Ms. Zhu,

802
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,559
I'm Mrs. Ruan.

803
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:38,519
Nice to see you.
Give me two more vegetable dishes.

804
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:40,200
Okay.

805
00:33:42,119 --> 00:33:42,759
Since we're here,

806
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:44,559
make up for all the drumsticks

807
00:33:44,799 --> 00:33:45,720
I didn't get to eat back then.

808
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:47,920
Yum!

809
00:33:48,279 --> 00:33:48,799
Good, huh?

810
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,279
Huaishi, we're leaving.

811
00:33:58,000 --> 00:33:58,359
Brother,

812
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,359
right here.

813
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:08,440
What's wrong?

814
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,840
Mom, you eat more.

815
00:34:11,239 --> 00:34:12,159
You'd look better with some weight.

816
00:34:12,559 --> 00:34:13,320
You just said
you were hungry and wanted

817
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:15,519
three drumsticks.

818
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:16,920
Lost your appetite already?

819
00:34:17,239 --> 00:34:17,760
How can I finish
three all by myself?

820
00:34:19,159 --> 00:34:21,079
[Why is Xu Huaisong here?]

821
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:22,639
[I just dodged]
[his questions last time.]

822
00:34:24,599 --> 00:34:25,559
[If he sees me sitting]

823
00:34:25,559 --> 00:34:27,079
[in the No.1 High cafeteria,]

824
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:28,719
[across from]

825
00:34:28,719 --> 00:34:30,400
[his old Chinese teacher.]

826
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:32,360
[He's going to figure out]
[I went to No.1 High.]

827
00:34:34,159 --> 00:34:35,039
[Then he'll ask me]

828
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,480
[what year, what class.]

829
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,280
[He might remember something he shouldn't.]

830
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:43,320
You know,

831
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:44,960
back when I was young,

832
00:34:46,239 --> 00:34:47,119
your father said

833
00:34:48,079 --> 00:34:49,159
I looked like Xue Baochai.

834
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:50,760
I'll send you the revisions

835
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:51,360
later.

836
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,559
Okay, bye.

837
00:34:55,280 --> 00:34:57,079
Brother, why are you suddenly back?

838
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,400
Felt like it.

839
00:34:59,039 --> 00:35:00,880
Let's go have hot pot

840
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,360
for winter solstice tonight.

841
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:02,760
How about it?
Tonight?

842
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:04,880
I'm busy.

843
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:06,079
Liar.

844
00:35:06,639 --> 00:35:07,519
You're clearly free.
You're watching me eat.

845
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,320
Who said I came to see you?

846
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,320
Do you have another
sister at No.1 High?

847
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:21,280
Stop looking around.

848
00:35:21,719 --> 00:35:22,519
Just eat.

849
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,239
It's really good.

850
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:32,159
I'm leaving.

851
00:35:34,039 --> 00:35:35,760
So soon?

852
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:37,440
Go back to class after lunch.
Get some rest.

853
00:35:39,559 --> 00:35:40,880
Wait for me.

854
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:45,199
Yu,
I'm going to see

855
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:46,960
Ms. Li later.

856
00:35:47,079 --> 00:35:48,039
You go take a walk around.

857
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:54,480
It's good?

858
00:35:56,239 --> 00:35:57,199
I'll have one.

859
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,400
There you go.

860
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:00,239
Just eat it if you want.

861
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:02,800
Knew you couldn't resist.

862
00:36:08,119 --> 00:36:08,719
Down low.

863
00:36:12,119 --> 00:36:12,840
Pass it to me.

864
00:36:15,079 --> 00:36:15,480
Come on.

865
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:16,760
Defense! Defense!

866
00:36:20,719 --> 00:36:21,480
Left foot, go.

867
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,400
Nice.

868
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:24,599
[December 21st. Winter Solstice.]

869
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:25,960
[Sunny.]

870
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:28,440
[Today I went back to Su City No.1 High.]

